column7:
You can follow me on Twitter at: https://twitter.com/Marshall_Dyer

Welcome to my playthrough of Soma, a sci-fi horror game from Frictional Games, makers of Amnesia: The Dark Descent and the Penumbra series.

Learn more about the game at:
http://somagame.com/

You can buy it from:
http://store.steampowered.com/app/282140/
http://www.gog.com/game/soma
https://www.humblebundle.com/store/p/soma_storefront

It is also available on PS4.

Playlist:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLzDeS-SWRIMMwKXpm4CDXMXfUiobAsvcZ

You can follow me on Twitter at: https://twitter.com/Marshall_Dyer
